        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长官此路难行。行个方便罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "难行也要行。众鬼卒拉着走。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众小鬼内同应。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苦啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "刘青提未起身珠泪伤惨，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众小鬼内同喝。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "二黄快三眼板",
          "musical_style": "二黄快三眼板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "想起了当年事好不心烦。\n十八岁进夫门配结良缘。\n生一子无踪影绝了香烟。\n在中年饮酒开荤打僧骂道改变心田。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众小鬼 （内同白） 走啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "何苦他用言语苦苦相劝，\n到如今铁树开花方可见天。\n从此后破了杀戒开了五荤，不信神佛咒骂青天。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众小鬼内同喝。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "阎罗王差五鬼白昼活现，\n才将我三魂七魄拿在阴间。\n叹人生如泡如影如幻如梦，果然有报应循环。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众小鬼 （内同白） 走啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "在阴间见了些剑树刀山，\n在阴间见了些剥皮把草嵌；\n行善的到阴间依旧行善。\n左金童右玉女，黄幡宝盖金罗伞，他好不威严。\n到如今项带长枷身披铁练，一步一打一张一扑获罪于天。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众小鬼内同喝。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "今日里解酆都游过五殿，\n眼前边黄沙滚黑雾漫漫。\n哪管他路难行扑打向前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "又只见黑暗暗一座高山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长官，前面什么所在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼恶狠狠执定铁练、走的我遍体疼魂飞魄散、大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前面叫做滑油山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我可从此经过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正要打此经过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此山高大，有些难过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "难过也要过。\n众鬼卒拉住走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苦啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听说要过滑油山，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘青提上桌子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不由刘氏心胆寒。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘青提跌下桌子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "跤跌在地平川。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎长官，我浑身疼痛，行个方便罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这泼妇不打不行。\n众鬼卒与我拉走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，苦啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大鬼拉刘青提同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "大鬼→刘青提",
          "turns": 8
        },
        {
          "edge": "刘青提→大鬼",
          "turns": 7
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 18,
