    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "儿求佛尊将娘搭救",
        "刘青提",
        "大鬼",
        "娘不该在佛前我就将誓盟就",
        "娘说道吃长斋恤老怜幼",
        "娘说道阴曹府报应无有",
        "小鬼",
        "我的儿到酆都城将娘搭救",
        "扁毛倒有修行意",
        "目莲僧"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "数板",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阎君命我作鬼头，十鬼见了九鬼愁。行善的金桥走，作恶的打不休来骂不休，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪怕小鬼作对头。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我乃大鬼是也。阎君朝拜佛祖去了，命我看守酆都城。不免在此伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（目莲僧上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿弥陀佛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "在仙山奉了师父命，\n来到阴曹探望娘亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小生目莲僧。奉了师父之命，来到阴曹探望娘亲，就此走走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "西方路上一只鹅，\n口含仙草念弥陀。\n人不修来待如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是酆都城。待我念起咒语。唵嘛呢叭咪吽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "扁毛倒有修行意、大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，哪里这样惊天动地，待我看来。\n原来是小师父，姓甚名谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小生目莲僧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长官听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "在仙山奉了师父命，\n来到阴曹探望娘亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你母亲姓甚名谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我的母并非是别的名姓，\n刘氏青提就是我娘亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我与你问来。\n众鬼卒！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众小鬼内同应。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "里面可有个刘氏青提？她子目莲僧看望于她，有者即来答话。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内二黄摇板） 听一言不由我喜之不尽，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是小姣儿寻找娘亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的儿叫罗卜不叫莲僧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我母子见一面感你的大恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小师父，里面有一个刘氏青提，他子不叫目莲僧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫什么糖萝菔，醋萝菔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢是傅罗卜？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不错，傅罗卜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请上城楼，我母子相见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阎君知道，那还了得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "行个方便罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "使不得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唵嘛呢叭咪吽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎唷，不要如此。\n众鬼卒，将刘氏青提押上都城。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘氏上台子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一见母亲泪眼认，\n怎不叫人痛在心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长官，将我母亲焰火去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众鬼卒，将刘氏青提焰火去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "刘青提站都城混身颤抖，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罗卜！我儿！儿啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "二黄回龙",
          "musical_style": "二黄回龙",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "叫一声罗卜儿细听从头："
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "二黄正板",
          "musical_style": "二黄正板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "儿本是阳世人相隔幽冥，\n却缘何来到了酆都城楼？\n看不见小姣儿我两泪交流。\n竟变了那铁树开花不能保留。\n娘不该我在阳间打僧骂道、不济贫民、开了五荤，到如今我受此幽囚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的儿啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "儿的父修正道跨鹤西走，\n为娘我被阎君地府来收。\n又谁知到了阴曹早晚间我受的是蓬头丐面、披枷带锁、口含阴灯，等何时我才\n得出头？\n也不枉为娘我就盼儿在心头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，今当四月八日，阎君赴龙华大会去了。你可哀告长官，将为娘放出都城，\n我母子也好相见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "我的儿到酆都城将娘搭救、娘说道吃长斋恤老怜幼、娘不该在佛前我就将誓盟就、娘说道阴曹府报应无有、儿求佛尊将娘搭救、目莲僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长官。将我母亲放出都城。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阎君知道，那还了得。使不得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唵嘛呢叭咪吽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎唷，哎唷。不必如此。\n众鬼卒，将刘氏青提押出都城。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘青提下台子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罗卜！我儿！儿啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "只说娘阴曹府无报应，\n天网恢恢有神灵。"
